Design:

Clean and intuitive user interface
Adheres to Apple's Human Interface Guidelines
Proper use of platform features
No misuse of system-provided buttons
Legal:

Complies with all applicable laws and regulations
No intellectual property infringement
Privacy policy is in place and accessible
No facilitating illegal activities
Privacy:

Proper handling of user data
No unnecessary data collection
Data usage disclosure
Compliance with Apple's App Tracking Transparency requirements
App Store-specific requirements:

Accurate metadata
Clear app descriptions
Appropriate categorization
Suitable app preview and screenshots
